data.description: ** Ask about the Pathway to Prosperity grant of up to $10,000 for home buyers which is available for this home!!   Completely Renovated!   Central air and finished basement with a full bath, laundry and garage with an all-new interior down to the studs and new roof make this home a bargain!!      Modern and sophisticated.   You will want to invite your family and friends over to enjoy all the upgrades and extras your new home has to offer!! Two full baths, ceiling fans, recessed lighting throughout the house, new windows, new roof, new gas HVAC with new central air, new Insta-Hot water heater, new front patio, new finished basement with large all new full bath.    As you enter the home thru the new front door, the first thing you notice is how open and modern it feels.   Recessed lights and tons of sun make this something special.   New kitchen with granite counter tops, new appliances, stainless sink and granite windowsills tells you the detail story.  Large Master bedroom with recessed lighting and two closets, Full bath upstairs is all new with upgraded ceramic tiles and tons of space.   Ceiling fans in two other bedrooms and even a hall closet for linens.  Finished basement with recessed lighting, closet, beautiful full bath, laundry area, garage and new back door.   You won't be disappointed.   This home is eligible for a Prosperity Mortgage " Home Assist" Grant of up to $10,000 for qualified buyers which does not need to be paid back.   The Grant can be used for down payment or closing costs.   Please ask the listing agent about the details.
